{"type":"answer","id":3068,"parentType":"question","parentId":702,"uid":915,"contents":"只对几位领导人执政期间的相貌进行评价：<br>\n<br>\n我觉得腊肉是坠丑的，气质猥琐不想多说。邓公虽然奇矮，但面相还算和善。长者虽然长着一副蛤蟆脸，但是能看出来他是有很高知识水平的蛤蟆。胡的面瘫反而使他气质上高人一等，有领导人风范。包子就是典型的独裁者形象，满脸横肉，大腹便便，全身散发着没文化的土包子气质。<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/2b896d11ba9a092d898cdabb24c869f5.jpeg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/2b896d11ba9a092d898cdabb24c869f5.jpeg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/2b896d11ba9a092d898cdabb24c869f5.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/1e67fa4cea2c8f0764a475cf5c60dbb2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/1e67fa4cea2c8f0764a475cf5c60dbb2.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/1e67fa4cea2c8f0764a475cf5c60dbb2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/4e111bc033c10bd0a8b3a15647d7aedc.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/4e111bc033c10bd0a8b3a15647d7aedc.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/4e111bc033c10bd0a8b3a15647d7aedc.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/7e611121067473317dba261caca663a2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/7e611121067473317dba261caca663a2.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180509/7e611121067473317dba261caca663a2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-05-09","agreeCount":8,"discussionCount":0}